See Nurtec® ODT (rimegepant) 75 mg full PI at @nurtecodt_pi. #PfizerSponsored #NurtecODTPartner
 
My migraine attacks don't care if I want to make a video, which is why Nurtec ODT is always an important tool in my production kit. Nurtec ODT has been a beneficial medication in helping me treat my migraine pain, so I can get back to the serious business of having fun on the internet. It's also approved to prevent migraine attacks; it's the only migraine medication approved to do both, all in one.
 
Prescription only. Individual results may vary.
 
Nurtec ODT is for acute treatment of migraine and preventive treatment of episodic migraine in adults. Selected Safety Information: Don't take if allergic to Nurtec ODT. Allergic reactions can occur, even days after using. Allergic reactions include trouble breathing, rash, and swelling of the face, mouth, tongue, or throat. Most common side effects were nausea (2.7%) and indigestion/stomach pain (2.4%). Swipe for Full Important Safety Information. @nurtecodt
 
Visit nurtec.com and talk to your doctor for more information! #NurtecODT

EARNESTNESS TIME my first time doing 10 minutes of standup was supposed to be in August, and then I got COVID. I was so, so bummed, I'd been pounding the pavement at mics all summer, just writing and performing nonstop, and it felt like a huge set-back for me. Which is deeply funny, because since August I've performed at the Comedy Store, and at The Hollywood Improv three times — once in the main room. And I finally got to do my ten — a much MUCH better ten than I would have done in August — at @crowcomedy with @wittytittiescomedy last week, and boy it was worth the wait. I can't wait to laugh about all the other setbacks I encounter next year.  #ALSO BUY TIX FOR MY NEXT SHOW AT THE IMPROV WITH @mermaidcomedyhour on 1/8! (📸 by @jamesriosstudios and general ability to have accomplished any of this by @jennifersterger )
